START

Input student_GPA
Input student_skills
Initialize career_list
Initialize recommended_careers as empty list

WHILE more careers to evaluate DO

    Select next career from career_list

    IF student_GPA >= career.required_GPA THEN
        IF student_skills match career.required_skills THEN
            Add career to recommended_careers
        ELSE
            Continue to next career
        ENDIF
    ELSE
        Continue to next career
    ENDIF

END WHILE

Display message (recommended careers generated / process completed)

END

